15fFDu6&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f70f3086\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/4c2gWbS1B715fFDu6</a><br />\n<br />\n連登Post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1666510\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1666510</a>"},{"pid":"08f4a56356a6bcee20ee068687b01ee4384408ed","tid":1671632,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】區議會選舉入閘名單塵埃落定。<br />\n<br />\n參選南區海怡西的黃之鋒被裁定提名無效，成為今屆逾一千名參選人中唯一一名因為政見，而被取消参選資格的人，政圈內外都普遍認為，被DQ的人比想像中少，更有陰謀論指，有關方面不介意讓多些人入閘，是因為已決定會取消選舉。<br />\n<br />\n街頭衝擊持續，《政情》打聽，建制陣營以至京官一度考慮是否押後選舉，不過，現行選舉條例下，最多只能押後十四天，押後更多就涉及修例，議席或會有真空期，《政情》最新聽聞，建制陣營已「被通知」要以1124完成選舉為共同目標。<br />\n<br />\n《政情》向多名建制派打聽，他們都指北京擔心選舉一旦取消會損害國際形象，加上部分建制中人都分析選舉是民怨的出口之一，將反政府的情緒透過用選票去表達，擔心若取消選舉會將「和理非」推向激進。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，比起一個月前，建制派對選情較之前樂觀，因為有調查指出，不認同示威者暴力的市民增加，若暴力持續，建制派評估對他們或更有利，目前在區議會佔近七成議席的建制派，一度擔心會失守過半數，但最新評估大黨仍會重創，有信心建制派整體保得住過半數議席，料可穩住區議會大局。"},{"pid":"2ec597517ee2d7bc269e1b905a777b2c0f97251d","tid":1671632,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:58:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>主線速遞</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 11 &middot; 2 </span><br />\n求援國際 堅守自治</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 維園流水式集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678270/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">星期六 11 &middot; 9 </span><br />\n柏林圍牆倒塌30周年集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:30 中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">星期日 11 &middot; 10 </span><br />\n和平紀念日紀念活動</strong></span><br />\n- 10:30 中環和平紀念碑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1678139/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cb0c1d9c515fd0d74bd9ad10224351c37014c29a","tid":1671632,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSKH950.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSKH950.png&h=0771c7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJvHqEm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJvHqEm.png&h=b90dd842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">網上購買</span></strong><br />\nRoyal British Legion<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.poppyshop.org.uk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poppyshop.org.uk%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=c221605f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.poppyshop.org.uk/</a><br />\n<br />\nM&amp;S Online<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marksandspencer.com/hk/search?q=Poppy&amp;lang=en_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marksandspencer.com%2Fhk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DPoppy%26lang%3Den_HK&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=777e9d97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.marksandspencer.com/hk/search?q=Poppy&amp;lang=en_HK</a>"},{"pid":"86d42376d0f6e3396d50bf9b971c1343110e605a","tid":1671632,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb0c1d9c515fd0d74bd9ad10224351c37014c29a","tid":1671632,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSKH950.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSKH950.png&h=0771c7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJvHqEm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u